OL,3,CWhat does the 2024 Budget mean for
OL,4,CWales?
OL,6,FPoliticians and voters here in Wales
OL,7,Fare coming to terms with some of the
OL,8,Fbig changes in one of the most
OL,9,Fsignificant UK Government budgets in
OL,10,Frecent memory.
OL,12,FThe Chancellor of the Exchequer
OL,13,Fannounced a series of spending
OL,14,Fdecisions including increasing
OL,15,FNational Insurance Contributions for
OL,16,Fbusinesses aimed, she said, at
OL,17,F"rebuilding Britain".
