OL,3,CWhat does the 2024 Budget mean for
OL,4,CWales?
OL,6,FThere's more money for the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment: an extra #1.7bn in the
OL,8,Fnext financial year, the highest
OL,9,Fincrease since the Covid pandemic, and
OL,10,F#25m for coal tip safety here.
OL,12,FBut the Welsh Conservatives called it
OL,13,Fa "smash and grab budget" while Plaid
OL,14,FCymru said it would "feel like
OL,15,Fausterity to many".
OL,17,FThere's no doubting the significance
OL,18,Fof this budget, both in terms of the
OL,19,Fhuge amount of tax increases it
OL,20,Fincludes (#40bn) and in terms of what
OL,21,Fit means politically.
