OL,3,CWhat does the 2024 Budget mean for
OL,4,CWales?
OL,6,FIt sets the tone and direction for the
OL,7,Fnext five years at least and, Labour
OL,8,Fhopes, the next decade or more.
OL,10,FPolitically, that also involves
OL,11,Fdemonstrating that having Labour in
OL,12,Fgovernment at both ends of the M4 will
OL,13,Fmake a difference, hence #25m for coal
OL,14,Ftip safety, meeting a long-running
OL,15,Fdemand by the Welsh Government and in
OL,16,Fresponse to a direct request from
OL,17,FFirst Minister Eluned Morgan.
