OL,6,FHence, too, the headline figure of
OL,7,F#1.7bn extra for the Welsh Government
OL,8,Fover the next financial year, a higher
OL,9,Ffigure than the #170m in March's final
OL,10,FConservative budget and one that the
OL,11,FUK Government says is the highest
OL,12,Fannual settlement since devolution
OL,13,Fbegan 25 years ago.
