OL,3,CWhat does the 2024 Budget mean for
OL,4,CWales?
OL,6,FThose decisions will come in
OL,7,FDecember's Welsh budget. Whatever they
OL,8,Fare, Labour will need to show voters
OL,9,Fthat the relationship is benefiting
OL,10,FWales - an early electoral test is
OL,11,Flooming ever closer with polls
OL,12,Fsuggesting that the 2026 Senedd
OL,13,Felection could be incredibly difficult
OL,14,Ffor the party.
OL,16,FLabour's Welsh Secretary Jo Stevens
OL,17,Fsaid: "This Budget has delivered for
OL,18,FWales for the first time in a
OL,19,Fgeneration.
