OL,3,CWhat does the 2024 Budget mean for
OL,4,CWales?
OL,6,F"The biggest settlement since
OL,7,Fdevolution will provide a record boost
OL,8,Fto spending for the Welsh Government
OL,9,Fto support public services like the
OL,10,FNHS while thousands of working people
OL,11,Facross Wales will benefit from today's
OL,12,Fincreases to their wages.
OL,14,F"Little more than a week after the
OL,15,Fanniversary of Aberfan disaster it is
OL,16,Ffitting that we have committed #25m to
OL,17,Fmake coal tips safe. It is testament
OL,18,Fto the new relationship between the UK
OL,19,Fand Welsh government, based on
OL,20,Fcooperation, respect and delivery.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
