OL,3,CWhat does the 2024 Budget mean for
OL,4,CWales?
OL,6,F"We will also drive economic growth
OL,7,Fand support our world-leading Welsh
OL,8,Findustries with Investment Zones,
OL,9,FFreeports and funding for communities
OL,10,Facross Wales.
OL,12,F"We have prioritised money to support
OL,13,Four steel communities, with nearly
OL,14,F#100m to support workers and
OL,15,Fbusinesses.
OL,17,F"This Budget delivers on what's
OL,18,Fimportant to the people of Wales, and
OL,19,Fshows the difference we can make when
OL,20,Ftwo governments work together for the
OL,21,Fbenefit of all."
