OL,3,CWhat does the 2024 Budget mean for
OL,4,CWales?
OL,6,FOpponents are unimpressed.
OL,8,FThe Welsh Conservative leader in the
OL,9,FSenedd, Andrew RT Davies, said:
OL,10,F"Labour's smash and grab Budget will
OL,11,Fhave a devastating impact in Wales.
OL,13,F"This Budget is built on the back of
OL,14,Fkeeping pensioners cold this winter,
OL,15,Fand the National Insurance rise will
OL,16,Fbe an incredibly destructive jobs tax
OL,17,Ffor Wales' economy which is already
OL,18,Fstruggling after decades of Labour
OL,19,Frule.
