OL,3,CWhat does the 2024 Budget mean for
OL,4,CWales?
OL,6,F"Nobody is surprised that the UK
OL,7,FLabour Government has cut business
OL,8,Frates relief, just as they have done
OL,9,Fin Wales, further proving that the
OL,10,FLabour Welsh Government's abysmal
OL,11,Frecord is the blueprint for Keir
OL,12,FStarmer's party. And just like their
OL,13,Fassault on rural communities in Wales,
OL,14,Fnow Labour's change to inheritance tax
OL,15,Frules risks marking the end of the
OL,16,Ffamily farm."
