OL,3,CWhat does the 2024 Budget mean for
OL,4,CWales?
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Plaid Cymru's Treasury
OL,7,Fspokesperson Ben Lake called it a
OL,8,F"missed opportunity" that "falls short
OL,9,Fof the transformative change that was
OL,10,Fpromised during the General Election".
OL,12,FHe added: "Labour promised two
OL,13,Fgovernments working together, but it
OL,14,Fappears the Welsh Government was
OL,15,Fsidelined yet again by the UK
OL,16,FGovernment, as there is little good
OL,17,Fnews for Wales.
