OL,3,CWhat does the 2024 Budget mean for
OL,4,CWales?
OL,6,F"Despite promising that those with the
OL,7,Fbroadest shoulders would pay their
OL,8,Ffair share, changes to employers'
OL,9,FNational Insurance will
OL,10,Fdisproportionately hit businesses
OL,11,Femploying lower paid workers, which
OL,12,Fwill have an impact on people across
OL,13,FWales. Furthermore, changes to
OL,14,Fagricultural property relief will
OL,15,Fundermine the family farm model that
OL,16,Fis at the heart of Welsh agriculture.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
