OL,3,CWhat does the 2024 Budget mean for
OL,4,CWales?
OL,6,F"The uplift to Wales' block grant will
OL,7,Fnot rebalance Wales' fiscal
OL,8,Fsettlement. Welsh councils alone face
OL,9,Fa #559 million budget gap in 2025-26.
OL,10,FDespite promising to 'get to grips
OL,11,Fwith HS2', the Chancellor failed to
OL,12,Fdeliver the billions owed to Wales.
OL,13,FAdditionally, by keeping cuts to the
OL,14,Fwelfare budget planned by the
OL,15,FConservatives, failing to help
OL,16,Fpensioners keep warm this winter or
OL,17,Fbring an end to the two-child cap,
OL,18,Fthis will still feel like austerity to
OL,19,Fmany."
